ygData.messageBody:
--- Casparian <casp@...> wrote:
> Does anyone have any tips for the best place to be
> located at this
> lvl? Obviously I'd like to get to 16 soon to get
> breeze but at the rate
> I'm going, I'm either going to not move from low lvl
> 14, or go down to 13
> if I get killed any more in oasis :o(

I seem to remember that Kurn's tower was pretty fun at
that level. Another possibility would include the
Karanas (Norht at this level I think.) Good place to
get some cash and easy exp. would be killing wisps at
Erud's crossing, esp if you have a magic weapon.
Previous poster's points about Unrest are well taken.
Dungeons are fun if you are a chanter, and good
practice. Befallen 3rd floor would probably be still
ok for you as well. Maybe Crushbone in the castle.
What level is Kerra these days? Upper Guk would be
great, if you could find a group.

Treana
DE enchantress mainly living as a blue-nosed iksar
